{
  "taskId": "task_1778000624047_126",
  "requestedModel": "anti-claude-opus-4.6-thinking",
  "text": "문서를 확인했습니다.\n\n칸반 보드와 타임라인의 기본 UI 구현에 이어, PRD에 명시된 핵심 기능인 **신규 태스크 생성**과 **태스크 상세 조회** 기능의 프론트엔드 구현을 완료했습니다. 담당자는 DEV_ADVISOR(본인)이며, 즉시 개발을 진행했습니다.\n\n### **구현 내용**\n\n1.  **API 연동 확장**:\n    *   `api/client.ts`: 태스크 상세 조회를 위한 `getTask`와 신규 태스크 생성을 위한 `createTask` 함수를 추가했습니다.\n    *   `api/hooks.ts`: `useGetTask` (Query) 및 `useCreateTask` (Mutation) TanStack Query 훅을 구현하여 컴포넌트에서 API와 쉽게 상호작용할 수 있도록 했습니다.\n\n2.  **신규 페이지 및 라우팅**:\n    *   `App.tsx`: `/projects/:projectId/tasks/new` (생성) 및 `/projects/:projectId/tasks/:taskId` (상세) 경로에 대한 라우트를 추가했습니다.\n    *   `pages/CreateTaskPage.tsx`: 와이어프레임에 기반한 태스크 생성 폼을 구현했습니다. `useCreateTask` 훅을 사용하여 태스크 생성 성공 시 칸반 보드로 자동 복귀 및 데이터 갱신이 이루어집니다.\n    *   `pages/TaskDetailPage.tsx`: `useGetTask` 훅을 사용하여 태스크의 상세 정보(담당자, 설명, 결과물)를 조회하고 표시하는 페이지를 구현했습니다.\n\n3.  **기존 컴포넌트 연동**:\n    *   `pages/KanbanBoardPage.tsx`: 화면 우측 하단에 플로팅 액션 버튼(+)을 추가하고, 클릭 시 태스크 생성 페이지로 이동하도록 연결했습니다.\n    -   `components/kanban/TaskCard.tsx`: 각 태스크 카드를 클릭하면 해당 태스크의 상세 조회 페이지로 이동하도록 네비게이션 로직을 적용했습니다.\n\n아래는 작업 완료된 전체 코드베이스입니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/api/client.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Task, TaskStatus, Project, TimelineEvent } from '../types';\\n\\n// Mock API base URL\\nconst API_BASE_URL = 'https://api.mycrew.io/telegram/v1';\\n\\n// A simple fetch wrapper\\nconst apiFetch = async (endpoint: string, options: RequestInit = {}) => {\\n  const res = await fetch(`${API_BASE_URL}${endpoint}`, {\\n    ...options,\\n    headers: {\\n      'Content-Type': 'application/json',\\n      // 'Authorization': `Bearer ${getAuthToken()}` // Assume a function to get JWT\\n      ...options.headers,\\n    },\\n  });\\n  if (!res.ok) {\\n    throw new Error('Network response was not ok');\\n  }\\n  return res.json();\\n};\\n\\n// Existing functions (placeholders for compilation)\\nexport const getProjects = (): Promise<Project[]> => apiFetch('/projects');\\nexport const getTasks = (projectId: string): Promise<Record<TaskStatus, Task[]>> => apiFetch(`/projects/${projectId}/tasks`);\\nexport const updateTaskStatus = (taskId: string, status: TaskStatus): Promise<{ success: boolean }> => apiFetch(`/tasks/${taskId}/status`, { method: 'PUT', body: JSON.stringify({ status }) });\\nexport const getTimeline = (projectId: string): Promise<TimelineEvent[]> => apiFetch(`/projects/${projectId}/timeline`);\\nexport const postCommand = (projectId: string, command: string): Promise<{ message: string }> => apiFetch(`/projects/${projectId}/commands`, { method: 'POST', body: JSON.stringify({ command }) });\\n\\n// --- NEW FUNCTIONS ---\\nexport const getTask = (taskId: string): Promise<Task> => apiFetch(`/tasks/${taskId}`);\\nexport const createTask = (projectId: string, taskData: { title: string; description?: string; assigneeId: string }): Promise<Task> => {\\n  return apiFetch(`/projects/${projectId}/tasks`, {\\n    method: 'POST',\\n    body: JSON.stringify(taskData),\\n  });\\n};\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/api/hooks.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"import { useQuery, useMutation, useQueryClient } from '@tanstack/react-query';\\nimport { \\n  getProjects, \\n  getTasks, \\n  updateTaskStatus, \\n  getTimeline, \\n  postCommand, \\n  getTask, \\n  createTask \\n} from './client';\\nimport { TaskStatus } from '../types';\\n\\n// Existing hooks...\\nexport const useGetProjects = () => {\\n  return useQuery({ queryKey: ['projects'], queryFn: getProjects });\\n};\\n\\nexport const useGetTasks = (projectId: string) => {\\n  return useQuery({\\n    queryKey: ['tasks', projectId],\\n    queryFn: () => getTasks(projectId),\\n    enabled: !!projectId,\\n  });\\n};\\n\\nexport const useUpdateTaskStatus = (projectId: string) => {\\n  const queryClient = useQueryClient();\\n  return useMutation({\\n    mutationFn: ({ taskId, status }: { taskId: string; status: TaskStatus }) => updateTaskStatus(taskId, status),\\n    onSuccess: () => {\\n      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['tasks', projectId] });\\n    },\\n  });\\n};\\n\\nexport const useGetTimeline = (projectId: string) => {\\n  return useQuery({\\n    queryKey: ['timeline', projectId],\\n    queryFn: () => getTimeline(projectId),\\n    enabled: !!projectId,\\n  });\\n};\\n\\nexport const usePostCommand = (projectId: string) => {\\n  const queryClient = useQueryClient();\\n  return useMutation({\\n    mutationFn: (command: string) => postCommand(projectId, command),\\n    onSuccess: () => {\\n      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['timeline', projectId] });\\n      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['tasks', projectId] });\\n    },\\n  });\\n};\\n\\n// --- NEW HOOKS ---\\n\\nexport const useGetTask = (taskId: string) => {\\n  return useQuery({\\n    queryKey: ['task', taskId],\\n    queryFn: () => getTask(taskId),\\n    enabled: !!taskId,\\n  });\\n};\\n\\nexport const useCreateTask = (projectId: string) => {\\n  const queryClient = useQueryClient();\\n  return useMutation({\\n    mutationFn: (newTask: { title: string; description?: string; assigneeId: string }) => \\n      createTask(projectId, newTask),\\n    onSuccess: () => {\\n      // Invalidate and refetch tasks for the project to show the new task\\n      queryClient.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: ['tasks', projectId] });\\n    },\\n  });\\n};\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/App.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"import { Routes, Route, Navigate } from 'react-router-dom';\\nimport ProjectListPage from './pages/ProjectListPage';\\nimport ProjectDashboardPage from './pages/ProjectDashboardPage';\\nimport TimelinePage from './pages/TimelinePage';\\nimport KanbanBoardPage from './pages/KanbanBoardPage';\\nimport CreateTaskPage from './pages/CreateTaskPage';\\nimport TaskDetailPage from './pages/TaskDetailPage';\\n\\nfunction App() {\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-h-screen\\\">\\n      <Routes>\\n        <Route path=\\\"/\\\" element={<ProjectListPage />} />\\n        <Route path=\\\"/projects/:projectId\\\" element={<ProjectDashboardPage />}>\\n          <Route index element={<Navigate to=\\\"timeline\\\" replace />} />\\n          <Route path=\\\"timeline\\\" element={<TimelinePage />} />\\n          <Route path=\\\"board\\\" element={<KanbanBoardPage />} />\\n        </Route>\\n        \\n        {/* --- NEW ROUTES --- */}\\n        <Route path=\\\"/projects/:projectId/tasks/new\\\" element={<CreateTaskPage />} />\\n        <Route path=\\\"/projects/:projectId/tasks/:taskId\\\" element={<TaskDetailPage />} />\\n\\n      </Routes>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n}\\n\\nexport default App;\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/pages/KanbanBoardPage.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"import { DndContext, closestCenter, DragEndEvent } from '@dnd-kit/core';\\nimport { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';\\nimport { useGetTasks, useUpdateTaskStatus } from '../api/hooks';\\nimport KanbanColumn from '../components/kanban/KanbanColumn';\\nimport { TaskStatus } from '../types';\\nimport { Button } from '../components/ui/button'; // Assuming shadcn/ui component\\nimport { Plus } from 'lucide-react';\\n\\nconst KanbanBoardPage = () => {\\n  const { projectId } = useParams<{ projectId: string }>();\\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\\n  const { data: tasks, isLoading, isError } = useGetTasks(projectId!);\\n  const updateTaskStatusMutation = useUpdateTaskStatus(projectId!);\\n\\n  const handleDragEnd = (event: DragEndEvent) => {\\n    const { active, over } = event;\\n    if (over && active.id !== over.id) {\\n      const taskId = active.id as string;\\n      const newStatus = over.id as TaskStatus;\\n      updateTaskStatusMutation.mutate({ taskId, status: newStatus });\\n    }\\n  };\\n\\n  if (isLoading) return <div>Loading...</div>;\\n  if (isError) return <div>Error loading tasks.</div>;\\n\\n  const columns: { id: TaskStatus; title: string }[] = [\\n    { id: TaskStatus.TODO, title: 'To Do' },\\n    { id: TaskStatus.IN_PROGRESS, title: 'In Progress' },\\n    { id: TaskStatus.REVIEW, title: 'Review' },\\n    { id: TaskStatus.DONE, title: 'Done' },\\n  ];\\n\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"relative h-full\\\">\\n      <DndContext collisionDetection={closestCenter} onDragEnd={handleDragEnd}>\\n        <div className=\\\"flex gap-4 p-4 overflow-x-auto h-full\\\">\\n          {columns.map((column) => (\\n            <KanbanColumn key={column.id} id={column.id} title={column.title} tasks={tasks?.[column.id] || []} />\\n          ))}\\n        </div>\\n      </DndContext>\\n      <Button \\n        className=\\\"absolute bottom-20 right-4 rounded-full w-14 h-14 shadow-lg\\\"\\n        onClick={() => navigate(`/projects/${projectId}/tasks/new`)}\\n      >\\n        <Plus className=\\\"h-6 w-6\\\" />\\n      </Button>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\\n\\nexport default KanbanBoardPage;\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/components/kanban/TaskCard.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"import { useDraggable } from '@dnd-kit/core';\\nimport { CSS } from '@dnd-kit/utilities';\\nimport { Task } from '../../types';\\nimport { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardContent } from '../ui/card'; // Assuming shadcn/ui\\nimport { useNavigate, useParams } from 'react-router-dom';\\n\\ninterface TaskCardProps {\\n  task: Task;\\n}\\n\\nconst TaskCard = ({ task }: TaskCardProps) => {\\n  const { projectId } = useParams<{ projectId: string }>();\\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\\n  const { attributes, listeners, setNodeRef, transform } = useDraggable({\\n    id: task.id,\\n  });\\n\\n  const style = {\\n    transform: CSS.Translate.toString(transform),\\n  };\\n\\n  const handleCardClick = () => {\\n    navigate(`/projects/${projectId}/tasks/${task.id}`);\\n  };\\n\\n  return (\\n    <div ref={setNodeRef} style={style} {...listeners} {...attributes} onClick={handleCardClick}>\\n      <Card className=\\\"mb-2 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700\\\">\\n        <CardHeader className=\\\"p-3\\\">\\n          <CardTitle className=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">{task.title}</CardTitle>\\n        </CardHeader>\\n        {task.assignee && (\\n            <CardContent className=\\\"p-3 pt-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\\\">\\n                Assigned to: {task.assignee.name}\\n            </CardContent>\\n        )}\\n      </Card>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\\n\\nexport default TaskCard;\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/pages/CreateTaskPage.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"import { useState } from 'react';\\nimport { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';\\nimport { useCreateTask } from '../api/hooks';\\nimport { Button } from '../components/ui/button';\\nimport { Input } from '../components/ui/input';\\nimport { Textarea } from '../components/ui/textarea';\\nimport { Label } from '../components/ui/label';\\nimport { Select, SelectContent, SelectItem, SelectTrigger, SelectValue } from '../components/ui/select';\\n\\nconst CreateTaskPage = () => {\\n  const { projectId } = useParams<{ projectId: string }>();\\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\\n  const createTaskMutation = useCreateTask(projectId!);\\n\\n  const [title, setTitle] = useState('');\\n  const [description, setDescription] = useState('');\\n  const [assigneeId, setAssigneeId] = useState('');\\n\\n  // Mock member list for the assignee dropdown\\n  const mockMembers = [\\n    { id: 'user-ux-1', name: 'dev_ux' },\\n    { id: 'user-fullstack-1', name: 'dev_fullstack' },\\n    { id: 'user-backend-1', name: 'dev_backend' },\\n    { id: 'user-qa-1', name: 'dev_qa' },\\n  ];\\n\\n  const handleSubmit = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\\n    e.preventDefault();\\n    if (!title || !assigneeId) {\\n      alert('Title and assignee are required.');\\n      return;\\n    }\\n    createTaskMutation.mutate(\\n      { title, description, assigneeId },\\n      {\\n        onSuccess: () => {\\n          navigate(`/projects/${projectId}/board`);\\n        },\\n      }\\n    );\\n  };\\n\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"p-4 h-screen flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <header className=\\\"flex items-center justify-between pb-4 border-b\\\">\\n        <Button variant=\\\"ghost\\\" onClick={() => navigate(-1)}>Cancel</Button>\\n        <h1 className=\\\"text-lg font-semibold\\\">New Task</h1>\\n        <Button onClick={handleSubmit} disabled={createTaskMutation.isPending}>\\n          {createTaskMutation.isPending ? 'Creating...' : 'Create'}\\n        </Button>\\n      </header>\\n      <form className=\\\"py-4 flex-grow space-y-4\\\" onSubmit={handleSubmit}>\\n        <div>\\n          <Label htmlFor=\\\"title\\\">Title</Label>\\n          <Input id=\\\"title\\\" value={title} onChange={(e) => setTitle(e.target.value)} placeholder=\\\"Enter task title...\\\" required />\\n        </div>\\n        <div>\\n          <Label htmlFor=\\\"description\\\">Description (Optional)</Label>\\n          <Textarea id=\\\"description\\\" value={description} onChange={(e) => setDescription(e.target.value)} placeholder=\\\"Add more details...\\\" />\\n        </div>\\n        <div>\\n          <Label htmlFor=\\\"assignee\\\">Assignee</Label>\\n          <Select onValueChange={setAssigneeId} value={assigneeId} required>\\n            <SelectTrigger>\\n              <SelectValue placeholder=\\\"Select an assignee\\\" />\\n            </SelectTrigger>\\n            <SelectContent>\\n              {mockMembers.map(member => (\\n                <SelectItem key={member.id} value={member.id}>{member.name}</SelectItem>\\n              ))}\\n            </SelectContent>\\n          </Select>\\n        </div>\\n      </form>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\\n\\nexport default CreateTaskPage;\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/pages/TaskDetailPage.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"import { useParams, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';\\nimport { useGetTask } from '../api/hooks';\\nimport { Button } from '../components/ui/button';\\nimport { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from '../components/ui/card';\\nimport { Separator } from '../components/ui/separator';\\nimport { Badge } from '../components/ui/badge';\\nimport { Paperclip, Link as LinkIcon, FileText } from 'lucide-react';\\n\\nconst TaskDetailPage = () => {\\n  const { taskId } = useParams<{ taskId: string }>();\\n  const navigate = useNavigate();\\n  const { data: task, isLoading, isError } = useGetTask(taskId!);\\n\\n  if (isLoading) return <div>Loading task details...</div>;\\n  if (isError || !task) return <div>Error loading task.</div>;\\n\\n  const renderAttachment = (attachment: any) => {\\n    switch (attachment.type) {\\n      case 'image':\\n        return <img src={attachment.url} alt=\\\"attachment\\\" className=\\\"rounded-lg max-w-full\\\" />;\\n      case 'link':\\n        return <a href={attachment.url} target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" className=\\\"text-blue-500 hover:underline flex items-center gap-2\\\"><LinkIcon size={16} /> {attachment.url}</a>;\\n      case 'text':\\n        return <p className=\\\"text-sm p-2 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-700 rounded\\\"><FileText size={16} className=\\\"inline-block mr-2\\\"/> {attachment.content}</p>;\\n      default:\\n        return <p>Unsupported attachment type</p>;\\n    }\\n  }\\n\\n  return (\\n    <div className=\\\"p-4 h-screen flex flex-col\\\">\\n      <header className=\\\"flex items-center pb-4 border-b\\\">\\n        <Button variant=\\\"ghost\\\" onClick={() => navigate(-1)}>&lt; Back</Button>\\n      </header>\\n      <div className=\\\"py-4 flex-grow overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n        <div className=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\\\">\\n          <Badge variant=\\\"outline\\\">{task.status.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase()}</Badge>\\n        </div>\\n        <h1 className=\\\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\\\">{task.title}</h1>\\n        \\n        <Card className=\\\"mb-4\\\">\\n          <CardHeader><CardTitle className=\\\"text-md\\\">Details</CardTitle></CardHeader>\\n          <CardContent>\\n            {task.assignee && (\\n              <div className=\\\"mb-2\\\">\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Assignee</p>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300\\\">{task.assignee.name}</p>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n            {task.description && (\\n              <div>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm font-semibold\\\">Description</p>\\n                <p className=\\\"text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 whitespace-pre-wrap\\\">{task.description}</p>\\n              </div>\\n            )}\\n          </CardContent>\\n        </Card>\\n        \\n        <Card>\\n          <CardHeader><CardTitle className=\\\"text-md flex items-center gap-2\\\"><Paperclip size={18}/> Attachments</CardTitle></CardHeader>\\n          <CardContent>\\n            {task.attachments && task.attachments.length > 0 ? (\\n              <ul className=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n                {task.attachments.map((att, index) => (\\n                  <li key={index}>{renderAttachment(att)}</li>\\n                ))}\\n              </ul>\\n            ) : (\\n              <p className=\\\"text-sm text-gray-500\\\">No attachments found.</p>\\n            )}\\n          </CardContent>\\n        </Card>\\n\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  );\\n};\\n\\nexport default TaskDetailPage;\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/types/index.ts\",\n    \"content\": \"export enum TaskStatus {\\n  TODO = 'todo',\\n  IN_PROGRESS = 'in_progress',\\n  REVIEW = 'review',\\n  DONE = 'done',\\n}\\n\\nexport interface User {\\n  id: string;\\n  name: string;\\n  avatarUrl?: string;\\n}\\n\\nexport interface Attachment {\\n  id: string;\\n  type: 'image' | 'link' | 'text';\\n  url?: string; // For image and link\\n  content?: string; // For text\\n}\\n\\nexport interface Task {\\n  id: string;\\n  title: string;\\n  status: TaskStatus;\\n  assignee?: User;\\n  description?: string;\\n  attachments?: Attachment[];\\n}\\n\\nexport interface Project {\\n  id: string;\\n  name: string;\\n  lastActivity: string;\\n}\\n\\nexport interface TimelineEvent {\\n  id: string;\\n  eventType: string;\\n  data: any;\\n  actor: User;\\n  timestamp: string;\\n}\\n\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"07_OUTPUT/telegram-miniapp-frontend/src/components/ui/button.tsx\",\n    \"content\": \"// Placeholder for shadcn/ui Button\\nimport * as React from \\\"react\\\"\\nimport { Slot } from \\\"@radix-ui/react-slot\\\"\\nimport { cva, type VariantProps } from \\\"class-variance-authority\\\"\\nimport { cn } from \\\"../../lib/utils\\\"\\n\\nconst buttonVariants = cva(\\n  \\\"inline-flex items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-md text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50\\\",\\n  {\\n    variants: {\\n      variant: {\\n        default: \\\"bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90\\\",\\n        destructive: \\\"bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground hover:bg-destructive/90\\\",\\n        outline: \\\"border border-input bg-background hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground\\\",\\n        secondary: \\\"bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80\\\",\\n        ghost: \\\"hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground\\\",\\n        link: \\\"text-primary underline-offset",
  "processedBy": "ariDaemon-bridge (gemini-2.5-pro)",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-05T17:04:47.819Z"
}